<ext_description linkend="Product_categorization_mim.categories_of_product">
The <b>categories_of_product</b> function returns the set of product category names associated with the argument. 
The function evaluates the bag of instances of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_category"/> that are 
associated with the input <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product"/> through an instance of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_related_product_category"/>. 
The function returns the SET of STRING values stored in the <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_category.name"/> attribute 
of the instances of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_category"/> in the bag. 
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Product_categorization_mim.categories_of_product.obj">
the <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product"/> whose categories are searched.
</ext_description> 

